summary: A video shows a person cutting various abstract and natural phenomena represented as food items. The phenomena include a tsunami with fish, a tornado made of dust, a thundercloud with lightning, a meteoroid with glowing cracks, and a rainbow. The video transitions between these scenes, with on-screen text labeling each phenomenon and the creator stating that they failed on one of the attempts, asking viewers to follow for more and provide feedback on including fails.
